{"tid":1050480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［厲害了！！］華為：有證據表明美國政府涉嫌入侵華為服務器","createTime":"2019-03-07T02:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T07:34:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":28,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"160a465227c43ea04e6b41e9ae6111f513e2debb","tid":1050480,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"華為：有證據表明美國政府涉嫌入侵華為服務器<br />\n<br />\n環球時報 03月07日 10:18 關注<br />\n華為在深圳總部發佈會上向外界透露，華為有證據表明美國政府涉嫌入侵華為服務器。<br />\n<br />\n稍早前，華為在深圳總部發佈重要聲明：決定起訴美國政府。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/chanjing/gsxw/2019-03-07/detail-ihsxncvh0506816.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2Fchanjing%2Fgsxw%2F2019-03-07%2Fdetail-ihsxncvh0506816.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=27e0bc08\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/chanjing/gsxw/2019-03-07/detail-ihsxncvh0506816.d.html?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96077f109eaa46edbb2204cbdbe73a84e6e6380b","tid":1050480,"uid":155095,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:28:34.000Z","msg":"告返美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c34835471d5c354b68ca111cdedc7ca0a308ef","tid":1050480,"uid":48083,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"【華為大反擊】宣佈控告美國政府 禁聯邦機構買華為產品違憲<br />\n12分鐘前<br />\n即時兩岸<br />\n <br />\n中國電訊設備製造商華為今早宣佈，已入稟美國德州地區法院控告美國政府，指控他們禁止聯邦機構使用華為的產品，有關行為涉嫌違反美國憲法。<br />\n<br />\n華為在有關聲明中指，美國國會通過《國防授權法》，卻一直未能提供對華為涉嫌竊密指控的實際證據，也沒有給予華為辯護的機會，因此華為要以法律手段維護權益。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，德州是華為美國總部所在地。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190307/59339306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F59339306&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=14c957d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F59339306&h=cc0ec173\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190307/59339306</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac731fc4a9a899b029c5c9e6afa72b10e7c81a94","tid":1050480,"uid":113626,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:29:46.000Z","msg":"關稅全面實施25% <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8474447f70d8bfd6a030a60bada0a12ce1b62f7b","tid":1050480,"uid":14918,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:32:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美國國會</span>通過《國防授權法》\\<